<!--
	 =====================================================================================
	 TILEMAP FILE
	 
	 Defines a universal tilemap for use with the tetragon tile engine.
	 
	 id					The unique resource ID.
	 type				The type of the tilemap which is one of "orthogonal",
	 					"hexagonal" or "isometric". Only orthogonal is supported yet.
	 layerCount			How many tile layers the tilemap is comprising of.
	 width				The width of the tilemap, counted in tiles.
	 height				The height of the tilemap, counted in tiles.
	 
	 meta.name			Meta-name of the tilemap. Meta data is mainly used for editors.
	 meta.description	Optional description of the tilemap.
	 meta.author		Optional author name of the tilemap.
	 meta.keywords		List of optional keywords, separated by comma, that the
	 					tilemap can be associated with.
	 
	 mapProperties		These are a list of general properties which are supported
	 					by a tilemap, e.g. 'backgroundColor' and 'backgroundGradient'
	 					which affects the background of the whole map or soundID which
	 					can be used to set a sound ID of a loop that plays while the
	 					tilemap is displayed.
	 =====================================================================================
-->
